                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9768" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2450</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">571 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶香千年，三茶共舞：漳州天福茶业的文化、产业与科技统筹之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Millennium of Tea Fragrance, Triple Tea Synergy: The Integrated Path of Culture, Industry, and Technology at Zhangzhou Tianfu Tea Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仲建兰，陈晓健，张竞丹，卞梦琪，戴雨瑶，高杰，王健涛，许文慧，蔡艺专</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">漳州天福茶业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三茶统筹；资源协同；茶文化品牌；数字化转型；产学研合作</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Triple Tea Integration; Resource integration; Tea culture brand; Digital transformation; Industry-university-research cooperation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">漳州天福茶业有限公司（以下简称“漳州天福茶业”）致力于成为中国三茶融合发展标杆企业。公司在生产经营过程中，通过协调多方资源，以茶文化为根基、茶产业为核心、茶科技为驱动，构建了三者协同发展的生态体系，走出了一条独特的兴茶之路。本案例详细探讨了漳州天福茶业如何践行三茶统筹以及取得了怎样的效果。通过本案例，读者能够生动体会到资源理论与企业生产运营相结合所产生的作用和重大意义，并启发读者如何将资源理论深化运用在其他更多的领域。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Zhangzhou Tianfu Tea Industry Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Zhangzhou Tianfu Tea Industry&quot;) is committed to becoming a benchmark enterprise for the integrated development of China&#39;s three teas. In the process of production and operation, the company has coordinated multiple resources, with tea culture as the foundation, tea industry as the core, and tea technology as the driving force, to build an ecological system of coordinated development among the three, and has embarked on a unique path of promoting tea. This case study explores in detail how Zhangzhou Tianfu Tea Industry practices the coordinated management of three types of tea and what results it has achieved. Through this case study, readers can not only gain a deeper understanding of the concept and characteristics of three tea coordination, but also vividly appreciate the role and significance of combining resource theory with enterprise production and operation, and inspire readers on how to deepen the application of resource theory in other fields.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源基础观；协同效应；资源异质性；品牌价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
